parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Oil Leaks and Camshaft Seal Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil leaks can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of control and potential accidents. Additionally, oil leaks can cause damage to other engine components, resulting in costly repairs.

engine stalling
difficulty restarting the engine
oil spots under the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Timing belt tensioner failure can cause the timing belt to break, leading to engine damage and potentially causing the engine to stall.

decreased engine performance
